Output follow_and_pause.gif

Set Shell bash
Set FontSize 18
Set FontFamily "JetBrainsMono Nerd Font Mono"
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Padding 10
Type "peacock -f production.log"

Sleep 1s

Enter

Sleep 3s

Space 1

Sleep 1s

Type "/"

Sleep 500ms

Type@500ms "payments"

Sleep 3s

Escape

Sleep 1s

Space 1

Sleep 5s

Ctrl+C


